                "quality_rating": 1
            },
            {
                "comment": "Probably the worst Physics teacher I have ever had. He simply goes over derivations from the book, but in a very hard to follow manner. His homework often simply doesn't ask questions with no explanation. His tests also are on topics not convened in class at all. Avoid him if you can.",
